{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act39side", "eventName": "出蒼白海", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EP-ST-3", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "永別了，大地", "storyInfo": "跟隨哈維爾的船員們回到鎮子，跟隨胡安娜的船員們準備與棘刺一同出海，帕斯卡拉去尋找她的好生活，每個人都選擇了各自想要的未來。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g13_ibtown_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "半個月後", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只剩下這一艘完好的鹽船，其他的多多少少都有受損，但大部分構件和材料都能拆下來用。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這本是鹽船的設計圖紙，上面多多少少附帶了一點開船技巧。這張是鹽漠地圖。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，好，我都要！要是真的能從鹽漠裡走，商隊能省不少時間！", "name": "興奮的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你開個價吧，我們乾脆一點！", "name": "興奮的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1590_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要這個數字，全用多布隆金幣結算。", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，沒問題！", "name": "興奮的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，你看看，金額對不對？", "name": "興奮的商人"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……沒錯。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好！那我先走了，你們繼續忙！", "name": "興奮的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1590_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個人怎麼這麼爽快……哈維爾，我是不是要少了？", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#6$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#7$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，等等！", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……怎麼了？", "name": "興奮的商人"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈維爾追上去兩步，順著繩子爬上了甲板。"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g3_newdeck_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個舵輪我留下了！多少錢？我退給你！", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，哦，舵輪啊！這可是一艘船上最重要的東西呢。", "name": "商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想要拿回去？那我要——", "name": "商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個數字。", "name": "商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#9$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，表情別這麼難看啊，老兄！剛剛交易已經完成了，它們現在是我的船了，對吧？", "name": "商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公平交易嘛，看它在你心裡值不值得這個價格了！", "name": "商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……算了……", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#7$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜啊，那下次有機會再交易囉。", "name": "興奮的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1256_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g13_ibtown_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——船員們！都過來吧！", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些就是剛剛賣鹽船得來的錢，我們平分，一人一份。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿了這筆錢，就去做你們自己想做的事情吧。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，魯斯，你的份。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1590_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#6$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#10$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1590_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實在的，我還沒有想好我接下來要去做什麼。", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#6$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做個決定，很簡單的事情。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#2$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1590_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……之前，我想的是離開胡安娜，安穩一點。後來我覺得你也是個瘋子，跟著你也不會安穩。", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#2$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我站在這個鎮子裡，看著鎮上這些人，又瘦又乾，眼睛裡一點光都沒有……在這裡過日子真的安穩嗎？", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#2$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我不在這裡，去別的地方，以我那些海盜的本事，能過得上安穩的日子嗎？", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#2$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1590_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說出來不怕你取笑，我其實蠻佩服蒂奇的。她比我大幾歲，一直都很有主見。", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#2$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天，我看到她傷成那樣，還是打定主意要跟著胡安娜出海……真倔強啊……也真夠厲害的，我可能就沒這個膽子。", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#2$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1590_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈……不說我了。你呢，哈維爾？", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#5$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我應該會換個地方開個餐館吧。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#2$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1590_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……就這樣吧，抽完這支菸，我也要上路了。", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#5$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人嘛……誰又能知道呢？", "name": "魯斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1590_1#5$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鹽船逐漸遠去，哈維爾望著那白色的風帆和魯斯的背影一同消失在視線裡。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他把自己的那份錢收進口袋，朝著下一個路口，走遠了。"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert_3", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，這個多少錢？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#10$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_006", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個銀幣。", "name": "車隊的商販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_006"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個呢？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#10$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_006", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是一個銀幣。", "name": "車隊的商販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_006"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，不貴嘛！", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#7$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這個、這個和這個，都幫我包起來，放到我後面這輛車上。", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#7$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_006", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒問題！哎呦，您買這麼多東西，這是要去哪裡啊？", "name": "車隊的商販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_006"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想要就買了，怎麼了？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#8$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_006", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼啦，您看到什麼想要的直接和我說就好！我都包好了送到您的車上！", "name": "車隊的商販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_006"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼哼，這還差不多。", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#7$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……買了衣服買了首飾還買了各種小東西……怎麼還是感覺少了點什麼……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#6$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……少了點什麼呢……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#6$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#6$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）……對啊，你也很震驚吧！", "name": "車隊成員A"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）但我怎麼知道會這樣啊？天啊……", "name": "車隊成員B"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（……嗯？他腰帶上的那個扣子真好看啊……亮晶晶的……）", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#4$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（是什麼做的，金屬？寶石？……好想要……）", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#4$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-50,-20", "duration": 2.5, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（好想要啊……）", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）……那只不過是他們在路上偶然發現的東西，就挖出來帶上了，想說隨便賣點錢……", "name": "車隊成員A"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）有人收嗎？真沒想到……", "name": "車隊成員B"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（沒注意到我，馬上就能拿到了……）", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）……誰能想到他們居然開了這個價錢……這個數字！你下半輩子都不用煩惱了！", "name": "車隊成員A"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）所以我們這次去也是做這個的？", "name": "車隊成員B"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嘿……到手！）", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）對……去哥倫比亞，我們賺筆大的……", "name": "車隊成員A"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#15$1", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（賺筆大的？）", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#15$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕斯卡拉把手一鬆，扣子穩穩地回到了那人的腰帶上。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼賺筆大的？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#15$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#15$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！", "name": "車隊成員A&B"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼偷聽別人說話！", "name": "車隊成員A"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿。", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#3$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是別人，我可是不會這樣搭話的，但兩位老兄，看起來極為出眾，很不簡單啊。", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#3$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我才敢這樣冒昧上前……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#17$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我的路費，去哥倫比亞這麼遠，路上無聊，兩位老兄也跟我說說吧？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#17$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g6_olddeck_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_avg_pirate_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1580_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1580_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夫人，我們真的要出海了嗎？", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#4$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……居然真的會有這樣的一天……", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#4$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，是的，小珍珠，我們是要出海了。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1580_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……真不敢相信……", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#5$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡安娜整理了一下被風吹亂的頭髮，望向身後。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多，這下子我們真的一無所有了，但我打定主意想要出海。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還願意和我們一起走嗎？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡安娜女士……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以當我的大副嗎？", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，我的船長，準備好了……嗯？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shipcannon", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我的老朋友在鬧脾氣了……讓我看看有什麼辦法能讓她消消氣。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g6_olddeck_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1580_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#6$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這個幾十年的老傳動核心，果然還是承受不住新裝的動力系統嗎……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1580_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶……溫蒂已經乘著她改造的小艇回去了，我們只好自己修修看了。船上還剩什麼材料？", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#6$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多，你的那個包包裡有什麼東西，怎麼這麼鼓？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是極境之前塞給我的東西，但都沒什麼用，我都不知道到底是……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先拿出來看看，說不定有用呢。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$aluminum"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多打開自己的背包，裡面塞滿的東西一下子全掉了出來。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡安娜和蒂奇湊上前去，翻看了起來。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？維生素片？這個是出海需要的東西啊！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1580_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通訊設備和防水靴也是……", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#3$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些工具……好像可以拿來修船。", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#3$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，極境這小夥子真可靠，這些東西現在可不好找啊。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1580_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩樣我先拿走了，應該能解決一下剛才的問題。", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#5$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你的表情，你不知道這些事？這麼多東西，難道是我們分開的那天他給你的？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……那天我們沒有道別。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前段時間，他隔一陣子就塞給我一個，我都放到背包裡了。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來，他早就看出來了。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至，比我自己還要早。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的好兄弟還能看不出你的心思嗎？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，問題解決了！", "name": "蒂奇"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解決了？那我們可以出發了嗎？", "name": "激動的船員"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呦呼——", "name": "興奮的船員"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出海——出海——出海——！", "name": "興奮的船員"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cheer_street"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧，船長，該決定我們航行的方向了。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多從胡安娜的手中接過望遠鏡。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無垠的鹽漠上鹽粒隨風翻湧，像雪白的浪花，但他的視線飛快地掠過了這片虛假的海，投向極遠處的天邊，投向那一抹亮藍的棲所。"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他獨自一人站在了船頭，伸出自己的手臂，看著上面的光芒流轉，等待著它給出一個方向。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g14_ibtown_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他站在街上，剛剛合起了手掌，夜空中最後一粒星光的碎屑也消散殆盡，黑暗再次籠罩下來。"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煙火結束了，我們走吧？", "name": "害羞的孩子"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧走吧，該回家了。", "name": "驚喜的路人"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼……", "name": "冷漠的路人"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "路人們紛紛散去，曾因他而聚集起來的人們，又離開了他。"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "小伊西多"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g6_olddeck_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡安娜見他遲遲沒有反應，便大步上前，蒂奇也跟著踏上了艦艏的甲板。"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船員們一個接一個地湊上前去，想看看他們的新船長究竟看到了什麼。"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，伊西多的身邊圍滿了人，走在後面的船員不得不伸長脖子擠進人群中。"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼，什麼？船長你到底在看什麼？", "name": "好奇的船員"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是還沒有找到方向嗎？", "name": "著急的船員"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "往哪裡開才是海？我們現在開的方向對嗎？", "name": "疑惑的船員"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多沒有回答他們的問題，他只是專注地看著自己的手臂。"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它怎麼一直在轉來轉去的？", "name": "疑惑的船員"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它什麼時候才會指方向啊？哪裡才是我們要去的地方呢？", "name": "著急的船員"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……我們會去向哪裡呢？", "name": "好奇的船員"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別急，別急，我們的船長會告訴我們答案的。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼現在……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該去往的方向是哪裡呢？", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彷彿是在回答他的提問一般，他手臂上的流光不再毫無規律地遊走，而是筆直且堅定地向天邊漾起漣漪。"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他嚮往著和身邊這群夥伴一起開向那傳說中廣袤無垠的海洋，於是心相原質為他指出了大海的方向。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船員們歡騰起來，蘭姆酒潑灑出來——"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡！是那邊！", "name": "興奮的船員"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是大海！", "name": "激動的船員"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人的目光都聚集在伊西多的身上。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下令吧，船長！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船員們的手中已經拿上了帆繩，胡安娜的手也放在了舵輪上，只等他一聲令下。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多深吸一口氣，回頭望向那些期盼他開口的真誠目光，他發自內心地感到，自己此刻不再害怕承擔起這份期盼。"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鹽漠上的風吹向他，他覺得如釋重負。"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船員們！", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拔起船錨，升起船帆——", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——我們出海！", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oicrwd"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出海——", "name": "船員們"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿——呦——！♪", "name": "船員們"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_turnrudder_2", "channel": "4"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "57_i13", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "xFrom": 0.0, "duration": 60.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_avg_chasing_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_largesail_wind", "channel": "3"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sandship_fast", "channel": "5", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ship_sand", "channel": "1", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "升起船帆嘿，收起船錨嘿♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "讓狂風撕扯我們的衣衫♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "讓暴雨澆醒我們的酒意♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "準備！出發！港口的船有千千萬萬隻！♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要和海浪搏鬥！我要在風浪上航行！我要與雷電擊劍——", "name": "亢奮的船員"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要找到埋藏在深海的寶藏！閃閃發光的金幣！", "name": "激動的船員"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是……但是……我剛剛在想，我們現在因為想要一起出海才聚在了一起……", "name": "猶豫的船員"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會不會未來有一天，我們有了不同的想法，就不會再在一起了？", "name": "猶豫的船員"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哈哈，未來？那也離現在太遠了，小子！", "name": "蒂奇"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論未來會怎麼樣，現在我們是在一起的，我們會一同出海！", "name": "蒂奇"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別想那麼多，拉緊你手裡的帆索！", "name": "蒂奇"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多船長，酒已經在手中，來說一句吧！", "name": "胡安娜"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多站上船頭，空氣中的水氣逐漸豐盈起來，他感受到了這種令人興奮的潮濕。"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敬遠方。", "name": "伊西多"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "5", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g6_olddeck_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_piratepet_vo01"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哼哧……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哼哧……哼哧……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？什麼聲音？怎麼這麼熟悉……？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_piratepet_vo01"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哼哧……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1586_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啾嘰！", "name": "寶寶"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1586_1#1$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寶寶？！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1"}, {"id": 457, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寶寶！你還活著！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#3$1"}, {"id": 459, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1586_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（狂舔胡安娜的臉頰）", "name": "寶寶"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1586_1#4$1"}, {"id": 461, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔唔……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#12$1"}, {"id": 463, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是來和我們一起出海的嗎？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 465, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1586_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（興奮地彈來彈去）", "name": "寶寶"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1586_1#1$1"}, {"id": 467, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，你真是我的好寶寶！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#3$1"}, {"id": 469, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g1_saltdesert_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 477, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 478, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_sand02", "layer": 1.0, "flip": 1.0}}, {"id": 479, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sand_lp", "channel": "2", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 480, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 481, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 482, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一道血痕從氤氲的蒸汽中延伸開來，蔓延到無邊無際的鹽漠深處。"}}, {"id": 483, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冰冷的舌頭品嚐著口腔中的血腥，殘缺的四肢由一股無主的強烈欲望驅使著向前挪動。"}}, {"id": 484, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不遠處，一條觸肢掙扎著破開鹽層，向著牠久違的日光蠕行。而後是第二條、第三條……"}}, {"id": 485, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一股無主的強烈欲望驅使著暗淡的發光器官向太陽高高揚起，彷彿要從中借得光芒。"}}, {"id": 486, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 487, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bonrcver"}}, {"id": 488, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 489, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bonbrke"}}, {"id": 490, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 491, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 492, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bonbrke"}}, {"id": 493, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 494, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 495, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只是想活下去，牠也只是想活下去。"}}, {"id": 496, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不擇手段，不擇形態。"}}, {"id": 497, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人的殘軀與海嗣的殘骸掙扎著，蠕動著，饑渴地互相吞噬。"}}, {"id": 498, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠們將永生地行走大地。"}}, {"id": 499, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 500, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "2", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 501, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 502, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 503, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 504, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 505, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 506, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 507, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 508, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}